      "role": "user",
      "content": "yeah i get the glove thing. but if nothing is actually \"connected\" physically through space, how does the information get there so fast? it's like something invisible is pulling the strings or something. is there any other way scientists describe that \"secret\" connection or the way things seem to happen behind the scenes?",
